0: ”Alexa, play President Joseph Fielding Smith talks”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: president joseph fielding smith talks
des: Select talks from Harold B. Lee, 10th President of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints. Talks include 'A Prophet’s Blessing', 'Eternal Keys and the Right to Preside', 'Counsel to the Saints and to the World', 'Let the Spirit of Oneness Prevail', 'Blessings of the Priesthood', 'I Know That My Redeemer Liveth', 'A Witness and a Blessing', 'Our Responsibilities As Priesthood Holders' and 'Out of the Darkness'.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
